# p3at_tutorial

Package demo for ROS navigation in Gazebo usingo Pioneer 3AT.

# obsavoid

Movimentacao do Pioneer 3AT com obstacle avoidance.

modulo do trabalho em src/obstacle_avoidance.cpp

Instalar previamente o turtlebot.

## Execucao

1. executar a simulacao do pioneer

$. roslaunch p3at_tutorial move_base_mapless_demo.launch

2. executar turtlebot_teleop para controlar o robo

$. roslaunch turtlebot_teleop keyboard_teleop.launch --screen

3. Executar o obstacle_avoidance

$. rosrun p3at_tutorial obstacle_avoidance


